('Galaxy note 8', 'The Galaxy Note8 is your portal to a new world when connected to this range of devices and interfaces. It\'s a world where boundaries are pushed and barriers broken so you can see more, share more, and do a whole lot more-effortlessly.More screen means more space to do great things. Go big with the Galaxy Note 8\'s 16.05cm (6.3 inch) screen. It\'s the largest ever screen on a Note device and it still fits easily in your hand. ', 'https://encrypted-tbn2.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcT_fL1WhrlcLDoVpDLND2rtnyfuq5EKiQC0wkFJjYsb1ox3wocEyILtaYR9', 67900),
('Galaxy S7', 'Samsung Galaxy S7 32GB smartphone - white offers incredible communication experience alongside insane entertainment. The dual SIM galaxy mobile runs on Quad-core (2.15GHz + 1.6GHz) Kryo processor and is based on Marshmallow Android 6.0 OS to power your needs perfectly. Storage and memory needs are met through 4GB RAM and built-in storage of 32GB with an extendable option upto 200GB via microSD slot. ', 'http://i.ebayimg.com/thumbs/images/g/X5cAAOSwKcdZvzXA/s-l200.jpg', 39990),
('Honor 6x', 'The dual lens 12MP + 2MP rear camera captures life’s magical moments in the highest definition to empower your inner photographer.\r\n\r\nNight Mode: 1.25um large pixel size for a better noise performance, even in low light\r\n\r\nSplash: An all-new splash function lets you isolate an individual color in monochrome images for greater artistic effect.\r\n\r\nHonor’s wide aperture range (F/0.95-F/16) lets you decide how much focus you want, and whether that shot calls for a stylish professional-grade blurred background effect.\r\n\r\nWith an ultra-fast focus time of 0.3 seconds, thanks to Phase Detection Auto Focus and a SONY IMX386 sensor, you will never miss that perfect picture opportunity again.\r\n\r\n', 'https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/proxy/h0g6ubyFyaTkskcj4znjkEF82iPmoG1fo-zYUYAKOAOOkVOgobD2Ra5RIid7Ay99i7j_CHm7GwxHt-Y80QlayrWm4UozvizZxOJj1N0pnspabnTI_NDnLXCJ50Towud1=w477-h308-nc', 12999),
('Honor 8', 'Honor 8 is powered by a 2.3 GHz octa-core CPU built on a 16nm architecture. 4GB of LPDDR4 RAM enables flawless multitasking and seamless gaming.\r\n\r\nThe CPU chipset contains an i5 co-processor, which controls Honor 8’s sensors and other features. The i5 co-processor works aligned with the Kirin 950 SoC chipset to increase processing speeds, response times and battery life.\r\n\r\nHonor 8 has a rapid smart file processing system for a smooth user experience.\r\n\r\n', 'https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/proxy/3kWAh_jLkmQdckw6xHnxEpB_LcbrrIzXlCivqFXHw7C7OHFw4GHN1OduxvNL1cB2w4KzDC066vbx8-CmD1oujPZ6DM_L-jD9mVsmc8LX5GsDkyzvL7si5zh4=w422-h349-nc', 14999),
