('Phab 2', 'The Lenovo Phab Plus\'s 17.27cm (6.8) Full HD display with IPS technology is not just big, it\'s also clever. With a crisp 326 ppi resolution.You can do so much more with the Lenovo Phab Plus, and it\'s got the battery power to match.There\'s also a front-facing 5-megapixel wide-angle lens to help you master the art of the selfie.', 'https://encrypted-tbn1.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSIBt5OK1_amQyG-UIvL-865bKVMwe2sJLEAmNMykVk-NhIrFIULc64OSEp', 13999),
