('Samsung Basic', 'Enjoy unlimited content and entertainment on your Samsung 100 cm (40 inches) 40M5100 Basic Smart Full HD LED TV. Connect your smartphone wireless to your TV and view on-demand content, videos, photos and listen to favourite music. Using the Smart Convergence technology and your smartphone\'s data (3G/4G/Wi-Fi), you can now cast your smartphone\'s content (YouTube, Amazon Prime, Netflix, Videos, Photos) on your TV.', 'https://static.rcwilley.com/products/110595289/Samsung-MU6300-Series-50-4K-UHD-Smart-TV-rcwilley-image1~200.jpg', 37690),
('Samsung J3 pro', 'HomeMobilesPhone FinderSamsungGalaxy J3 (6) Samsung Galaxy J3 (6) SPECIFICATIONS USER REVIEWS NEWS Galaxy J3 (6) Share on FacebookTweetShareShareEmailReddit Samsung Galaxy J3 (6) smartphone was launched in November 2015. The phone comes with a 5.00-inch touchscreen display with a resolution of 720 pixels by 1280 pixels. The Samsung Galaxy J3 (6) is powered by 1.5GHz quad-core it comes with 1.5GB of RAM. The phone packs 8GB of internal storage that can be expanded up to 128GB via a microSD card. As far as the cameras are concerned, the Samsung Galaxy J3 (6) packs a 8-megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 5-megapixel front shooter for selfies. The Samsung Galaxy J3 (6) runs Android 5.1 and is powered by a 2600mAh non removable battery. It measures 142.30 x 71.00 x 7.90 (height x width x thickness) and weighs 138.00 grams. The Samsung Galaxy J3 (6) is a single SIM (GSM) smartphone that accepts a Micro-SIM. Connectivity options include Wi-Fi, GPS, Bluetooth, NFC, FM, 3G and 4G (with support for Band 40 used by some LTE networks in India). Sensors on the phone include Proximity sensor and Accelerometer.', 'https://encrypted-tbn3.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQcM9QQ2Pqh3YytaWNWWzxCR5Zg_YOjnOoujuqUmp7JyQ2FMRRn', 6490),
('Samsung on5', 'An unprecedentedly thin frame and bezel for a comfortable and steady grip. Its eye-catching, leather-feel rear cover adds an extra touch of class.', 'https://image2.pricedekho.com/p/1/1/91/2321391/10340147-samsung-galaxy-on5-pro-black-picture-big.jpg', 7490),
('Samsung on7', 'Surf like a pro,Game like a pro,Ride like a pro', 'https://image3.pricedekho.com/p/1/0/90/2238290/10340099-samsung-galaxy-on7-pro-gold-picture-big.jpg', 8990),
('Sony Bravia ', 'Switch on to Sony full HD 1080p and experience sharper, clearer, more colourful pictures with five times the detail of standard definition TV. The new smartphone plug and play feature lets you enjoy all your smartphone contents with better picture and sound quality. Your TV is safeguarded against dust, lightning surges and humidity with X-Protection Pro and ready to entertain with features like FM radio and USB multi-format play.', ' https://www.avechi.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/SONY-55-Smart-4K-Digital-Full-HD-LED-Tv-..Android-Tv-x-reality-PRO-200x200.jpg', 41499),
('Vibe K5 Note', 'The phone combines brilliant performance with bargain pricing. Designed for multimedia enthusiasts on a budget, this lightweight smartphone offers 5-inch wide view HD displays for rich, smooth videos. 4G LTE connectivity and an optional octa-core processor deliver blazing speeds for the latest games. Dolby Atmos enhances the whole experience with dynamic sound.', 'https://image2.pricedekho.com/p/1/6/66/2174866/10055834-lenovo-vibe-k5-note-3gb-ram-silver-picture-big.jpg', 7999),
('Vivo V7+', 'This smartphone runs on Qualcomm Snapdragon 450 processor. This processor improves the overall user experience of the phone. It is based on the Android 7.1.2 Nougat operating system, which again has multiple features that improve the overall user experience. Vivo has added their own FunTouch 3.2 OS to the Android OS and improved the user experience of the device.', 'https://b6c18f286245704fe3e9-05e2055f4cd9122af02914269431c9f6.ssl.cf1.rackcdn.com/18152840_vivo-v7-plus-launches-officially-in_cec26446_m.jpg?bg=C4BDCB', 21990),
